#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:103
msgid "Bypass"
msgstr "Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:106
msgid "预加载"
msgstr "Preloading"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:107
msgid ""
"浏览器为了增强用户体验，让浏览器更有效率，就有一个预加载的功能，大体是利用浏览器空闲时间去加载指定的内容，然后缓存起来。这个技术又细分为DNS-"
"prefetch、subresource、prefetch、preconnect、prerender。"
msgstr ""
"To improve user experience and efficiency, browsers provide preloading. In "
"general, the browser uses idle time to load specified content and cache it. "
"This technique can be further divided into DNS-prefetch, subresource, "
"prefetch, preconnect, and prerender."

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:109
msgid "HTML5页面预加载是用link标签的rel属性来指定的。如果csp头有unsafe-inline，则用预加载的方式可以向外界发出请求，例如"
msgstr ""
"HTML5 page preloading is specified through the rel attribute of the link "
"tag. If the CSP header includes unsafe-inline, preloading can be used to send "
"requests to the outside, for example:"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:123
msgid "另外，不是所有的页面都能够被预加载，当资源类型如下时，将阻止预加载操作："
msgstr ""
"In addition, not every page can be preloaded. Preloading is blocked for the "
"following resource types:"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:125
msgid "URL中包含下载资源"
msgstr "The URL contains a downloadable resource"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:126
msgid "页面中包含音频、视频"
msgstr "The page contains audio or video"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:127
msgid "POST、PUT和DELET操作的ajax请求"
msgstr "Ajax requests using POST, PUT, or DELETE operations"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:128
msgid "HTTP认证"
msgstr "HTTP authentication"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:129
msgid "HTTPS页面"
msgstr "HTTPS pages"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:130
msgid "含恶意软件的页面"
msgstr "Pages containing malware"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:131
msgid "弹窗页面"
msgstr "Pop-up pages"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:132
msgid "占用资源很多的页面"
msgstr "Pages that consume many resources"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:133
msgid "打开了chrome developer tools开发工具"
msgstr "Chrome Developer Tools is open"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:136
msgid "MIME Sniff"
msgstr "MIME Sniff"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:137
msgid ""
"举例来说，csp禁止跨站读取脚本，但是可以跨站读img，那么传一个含有脚本的img，再``<script "
"href='http://xxx.com/xx.jpg'>``，这里csp认为是一个img，绕过了检查，如果网站没有回正确的mime "
"type，浏览器会进行猜测，就可能加载该img作为脚本"
msgstr ""
"For example, if CSP forbids cross-site script reads but allows cross-site "
"image reads, an image containing script can be uploaded and then referenced "
"with ``<script href='http://xxx.com/xx.jpg'>``. CSP treats it as an image and "
"the check is bypassed. If the site does not return the correct MIME type, the "
"browser may sniff it and load the image as a script."

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:140
msgid "302跳转"
msgstr "302 Redirect"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:141
msgid "对于302跳转绕过CSP而言，实际上有以下几点限制："
msgstr "A CSP bypass through a 302 redirect has the following practical limits:"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:143
msgid "跳板必须在允许的域内。"
msgstr "The redirector must be in an allowed domain."

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:144
msgid "要加载的文件的host部分必须跟允许的域的host部分一致"
msgstr ""
"The host part of the file being loaded must match the host part of the "
"allowed domain"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:147
msgid "iframe"
msgstr "iframe"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:148
#, python-format
msgid ""
"当可以执行代码时，可以创建一个源为 ``css`` ``js`` "
"等静态文件的frame，在配置不当时，该frame并不存在csp，则在该frame下再次创建frame，达到bypass的目的。同理，使用 "
"``../../../`` ``/%2e%2e%2f`` 等可能触发服务器报错的链接也可以到达相应的目的。"
msgstr ""
"When code execution is possible, a frame whose source is a static file such "
"as ``css`` or ``js`` can be created. If misconfigured, that frame may not have "
"CSP, and creating another frame inside it can achieve a bypass. Similarly, "
"links such as ``../../../`` or ``/%2e%2e%2f`` that may trigger server errors "
"can also be used for this purpose."

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:152
msgid ""
"当script-src为nonce或无限制，且base-uri无限制时，可通过 ``base`` "
"标签修改根URL来bypass，如下加载了http://evil.com/main.js"
msgstr ""
"When script-src uses a nonce or is unrestricted, and base-uri is unrestricted, "
"the ``base`` tag can modify the root URL to bypass CSP. The following example "
"loads http://evil.com/main.js."

