#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:162
msgid "可上传SVG时，通过恶意SVG绕过同源站点"
msgstr "When SVG upload is allowed, use a malicious SVG to bypass a same-origin site"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:163
msgid "存在CRLF漏洞且可控点在CSP上方时，可以注入HTTP响应中影响CSP解析"
msgstr ""
"When a CRLF vulnerability exists and the controllable point is above CSP, an "
"HTTP response can be injected to affect CSP parsing"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/csp.rst:164
msgid "CND Bypass，如果网站信任了某个CDN, 那么可利用相应CDN的静态资源bypass"
msgstr ""
"CDN Bypass: if a website trusts a CDN, the corresponding CDN static resources "
"can be used for a bypass"

